1 ) first keep ready the project 
2 ) Go to firebase console --> create a firebase project
        --> set the name
        --> continue
        --> continue
        --> continue
        select the account and press to create project
                                      -- >  continue

3) select the platform (like ios , android ,web, flutter etc)

now for web
-----------

--> Register the app
           --> give the name and check the box
           --> register app
           
for next step ( ADD FIREBASE SDK )

using now 
 use npm 
      run this in project directory 

       -->  npm install firebase

       and copy 
